window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>BARRICADE EVERY WINDOW. BOLT EVERY DOOR. A MANIAC IS ON THE LOOSE. </b><br> <br> Dive into the heart-stopping Maniac on the Loose saga, a three-book horror series that unleashes Ski Mask, a cunning psychopath with multiple lives and a deadly calling.<br> <br> In Maniac in the Shadows, a savage escapee from an insane asylum terrorizes a quiet town. The hospital’s ruthless director dispatches a merciless enforcer to silence the threat before the truth spills, weaving a chilling tale of predator and prey.<br> <br> 9 Lives of Ski Mask thrusts Ski Mask into perilous missions, from unraveling sinister plots in hidden enclaves to facing lethal challenges in hellish realms. As a psychiatric hospital’s grim enforcer, he stalks society’s darkest corners—but can his extra lives defy the horrors lurking?<br> <br> Return of the Maniac delivers the pulse-pounding finale, where betrayal and a treacherous shadow push Ski Mask to the brink. Racing to hunt a ruthless killer, his fractured focus threatens to make him a pawn in a maniac’s deadly endgame.</p> <p><b>Relentless, unpredictable, and brimming with suspense, the Maniac on the Loose series will seize your nerves from first minute to last.</b></p>"; 
